<li><a href="http://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/physics/General/LightMill/light-mill.html" class="external text" title="http://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/physics/General/LightMill/light-mill.html" rel="nofollow">How does a light-mill work?-Physics FAQ</a></li>
<li><a href="http://members.chello.nl/~h.dijkstra19/page7.html" class="external text" title="http://members.chello.nl/~h.dijkstra19/page7.html" rel="nofollow">The Cathode Ray Tube site</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/abstract/0959-5309/45/2/315" class="external text" title="http://www.iop.org/EJ/abstract/0959-5309/45/2/315" rel="nofollow">1933 Bell and Green experiment</a> describing the effect of different gas pressures on the vanes.</li>
